191
00:16:41,033 --> 00:16:42,898
To vazi i za tebe, Kurtis.

192
00:16:45,037 --> 00:16:47,062
Bog te nece ostaviti.

193
00:16:59,251 --> 00:17:00,479
Oprostite.

194
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:06,649
Moram popricati s nekim.

195
00:17:08,360 --> 00:17:10,885
Imam zamracenja koja ne mogu kontrolisati.

196
00:17:12,898 --> 00:17:17,301
Poðite samnom, gospoðo.
Da vidimo mozemo li vam pomoci, u redu?

197
00:17:23,909 --> 00:17:25,877
Provela sam detinjstvo u sirotistu.

198
00:17:27,346 --> 00:17:32,682
Kada me je moj muz, gospodin Karson, tada zaprosio,
bio mi je izlaznica odande.

199
00:17:32,785 --> 00:17:35,879
-Koliko ste tada imali godina?
-Trinaest.

200
00:17:37,489 --> 00:17:38,922
Bili smo sretni.

201
00:17:39,825 --> 00:17:42,817
Imali smo divan dom, dva divna decaka.

202
00:17:46,098 --> 00:17:47,190
A onda?

203
00:17:52,571 --> 00:17:54,334
Ne volim da govorim o tome.

204
00:18:01,947 --> 00:18:04,882
On je imao drugu zenu i decu.

205
00:18:09,455 --> 00:18:12,015
